POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ログイン
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "password123"
}

